race.comment: NORDIC INVADER (4) has laid a solid foundation for the longer sprint. Lightly raced and Wiggins sticking aboard is a positive. He's on a 9-day return and will be tough to beat in this lineup. ALABAMA MOONLIGHT (1) belted a CLB field at Atherton by 2.3L coming back to this distance. The in-form Morrison sticks and if he holds the form is a decent chance to repeat. FLOURISH (5) is fast and won her Maiden here 18 days ago. Has the rails gate and upside and can't be ruled out. GREY POWER (6) is third up and can show more today over the longer sprint. The blinkers come off, and she's likely to race forward.
